<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Director at Legendary Business Owners
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I help people become number 1 in their industry
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
Being number 1 is the only way I know to guarantee success. It means caring more about your customers or audience than anyone else in your industry.  Since that's what I also care about (and I made it to number 1 in my first company) I get more satisfaction in life now helping others achieve this than anything else I've ever done in over 3 decades in business.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
When a person is ready, the message makes sense.
</p>

